title: 334: Jujimufu- The Anabolic Acrobat
description: In this episode Sal, Adam and Justin interview Jujimufu, the Anabolic Acrobat. Jujimufu combines muscle, flexibility and acrobatics. He has been featured in a Taco Bell commercial and was a recent contestant on America's Got Talent. Jujimufu is also a Kimera Koffee athlete.
